metadata.name: Into the Unknown
metadata.description: As Electra and her familiar navigated the desolate industrial landscape, they stumbled upon a mysterious portal. The portal seemed to beckon to her with a siren's call, tempting her with the promise of adventure and discovery. With her feline companion by her side, Electra approached the portal with trepidation, unsure of what lay on the other side, but unable to resist its mysterious allure.
